emotes.msg: This is the gem from the core of the Nexus Crystal, is it not? A worthy achievement, indeed. I will make you the greatest suit of armor in Dereth.
Though it shames me to admit so, this gem is beyond my talents. I will not tamper with it. There are some gem collectors outside of Uziz, however, who may be able to help.

Nuhmudira has finally restored us to full health!  She has also stocked us with some extra supplies that we needed, such that we can provide you with either a version of the original Shadow Armor, or its successor.  If you wish to trade one version of your Celdon set for another, simply hand it to me.  Please take out all Atlan stones from your armor before handing it to me.

Also, if you wish to color your new Greater Shadow Armor, you may buy a vat of color from my assistant.  If you do not like the color, please give me the armor piece and I will replace it with the standard piece, which you may then choose to recolor.
A small gem. Hmph. Here is your lower-body armor. If you care to bring me another of these small gems, I can make upper armor as well.
Back for more, are you? Here is the upper-body armor to complete your lesser suit.
If you are so adept at slaying shadows and crystals, bring me a more powerful gem and stop bothering me with this detritus.
If you really must have another set of that inferior armor, however, give me this gem again and I will see what I can do.
A mediocre gem.  Take your reward. These leggings are of fair quality. I need another of those gems to make sleeves and a breastplate for you.
This gem allows me to complete the suit for you. Take it, and perhaps you can slay greater creatures and bring me a more powerful gem.
You have a complete suit already. Take this gem back.
If you really must have another set of that inferior armor, however, give me this gem again and I will see what I can do.
A very powerful gem indeed. This is the strongest armor I am able to craft. Bring me another gem to receive upper-body armor as well.
Excellent. I can complete your suit of armor now. This is the most powerful armor I am able to craft.
I have made you the best armor I can make.
